%% MLflow Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4/mlflow-operator.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin / User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as MLflow Operator<br/>controller-runtime
    participant Helm as Helm Renderer<br/>(in-process)
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP TLS
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collector

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Admin,Helm: Flow 1: MLflow CR Reconciliation
        Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update MLflow CR
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>Helm: Render chart templates<br/>(function call, in-process)
        Helm-->>Operator: Rendered manifests
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply resources<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Note right of Operator: Creates: Deployment, Service,<br/>NetworkPolicy, PVC, SA,<br/>RBAC, HTTPRoute, ConsoleLink,<br/>ServiceMonitor
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Admin,MLflow: Flow 2: Client Request via Gateway API
        Admin->>Gateway: HTTPS request to /mlflow/*<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Gateway->>MLflow: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Path rewrite: /mlflow/api/* -> /api/*
        MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Delegated user token
        K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Authorization decision
        MLflow-->>Gateway: API Response
        Gateway-->>Admin: HTTPS Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over MLflow,S3: Flow 3: Artifact Storage Access
        Admin->>MLflow: Upload/download artifacts<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: K8s RBAC
        MLflow->>S3: S3 API calls<br/>443/TCP or 9000/TCP<br/>HTTPS/HTTP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS credentials (env)
        S3-->>MLflow: Artifact data
        MLflow-->>Admin: Artifact response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over MLflow,DB: Flow 3b: Database Access
        MLflow->>DB: SQL queries<br/>5432/TCP (PostgreSQL) or 3306/TCP (MySQL)<br/>TLS verify-full (when CA configured)<br/>Auth: Connection string
        DB-->>MLflow: Query results
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over Prom,MLflow: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prom->>MLflow: GET /prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        MLflow-->>Prom: Metrics data
        Prom->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token + TokenReview
        Operator-->>Prom: Operator metrics
    end
